title: Red Bull Thre3Style Vancouver regionals for the World DJ Champs
description:
'47 Brand is the official hat and tee shirt of the Red Bull Thre3Style DJ Competition in Canada. This clip was taken from the regional round in Vancouver.

'47 Brand is a sports lifestyle brand based out of Boston. We're a proud partner of the NFL, MLB, NBA, NHL and over 900 colleges. Established in 1947.
